{"tid":2165737,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教局審查替政權洗白  通識教材指鹿為馬","createTime":"2020-08-20T04:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T04:23:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e6782fae5f085e9dcbd90d4d47db5d0d4f452e","tid":2165737,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/FDUQ3K2NWJGLFGG6HO6N6AHKSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FFDUQ3K2NWJGLFGG6HO6N6AHKSA%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufdKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=6a5e2793\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FFDUQ3K2NWJGLFGG6HO6N6AHKSA%2F&h=292a1f6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/FDUQ3K2NWJGLFGG6HO6N6AHKSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n教局審查替政權洗白 <br />\n通識教材指鹿為馬<br />\n<br />\n【洗腦教育】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：教協轟扭曲社會實況<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】教育局全力配合港共政權對下一代洗腦，肆意「河蟹」通識科政治內容。本報連日來檢視教育局日前公佈通識教科書修訂列表，揭發越來越多指鹿為馬的不實內容，替政權塗脂抹粉，如前特首梁振英收受澳洲企業UGL公司5,000萬元遭刪去；內地2003年涉隱瞞沙士一事遭竄改，輕描淡寫成「未有及時發佈資訊」。有通識教科書作者直斥當局行徑違背通識教育原意；有教師坦言無所適從，將自製教材彌補刪減的內容，讓學生知道事實真相。<br />\n<br />\n記者：關玉婷 鄧力行 張雅婷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dCW_IQaRKOMt6DOCrEK71ms0mtE=/3543x2362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NTKRLDGXMNB3XODCYR6TYEOIG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdCW_IQaRKOMt6DOCrEK71ms0mtE%3D%2F3543x2362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNTKRLDGXMNB3XODCYR6TYEOIG4.jpg&h=02556ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教育局長楊潤雄<br />\n<br />\n最新的通識科教科書修訂列表中，「今日香港」單元成為「河蟹」重災區。其中《明名高中通識教育》「應試特訓」練習中關。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教師：可自製教材助學生認識<br />\n<br />\n該書原版講述「獨立調查委員會」時，引用前特首梁振英收受澳洲企業UGL公司5,000萬元事件作例子，以及香港電視不獲發牌一例，惟在修訂版中同遭刪去。<br />\n<br />\n其他民生議題亦面對類似情況，如香港教育圖書公司（教圖）出版的《新視野通識教育．公共衞生》，介紹2003年沙士爆發時，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教協理事、通識科老師方景樂指出，香港有否三權分立具爭議性，但不能只保留親建制。。。。。。。。有權力可制衡。<br />\n<br />\n方坦言教育局刪改通識科內容會令教師無所適從，又認為教科書欠缺的部份，教。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者斥違反通識科設立目的<br />\n<br />\n其中一本通識教科書的作者Kitty（化名）直斥當局「𠵱家做緊嘅所有嘢，都係違反緊通識科設立目的同原意」，即希望學生能兼聽、兼。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港通識教育教師聯會指通識教育科課程運行逾10年，前線教師對課程有一定的掌握。聯會期望局方能提供建議教科書的修訂原則，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rTJEDbBE2xV9wiphhYoLKsqX5ow=/2448x1329/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QZR7X6LNTBAG5MYQO7C25ZVRUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrTJEDbBE2xV9wiphhYoLKsqX5ow%3D%2F2448x1329%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQZR7X6LNTBAG5MYQO7C25ZVRUY.jpg&h=36e4c6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【「河蟹」中國沙士責任】■教圖出版的《新視野通識教育．公共衞生》原版介紹沙士時，指中國隱瞞疫症及世衞事發三個月後才可到廣東調查，修訂後改成中國未有及時發佈資訊及有向世衞報告病例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/URqANkD159bu0Dgj3rXh6O7Ro0k=/1902x764/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X4RH5P5GIZEYJE24NTSFUW3IDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FURqANkD159bu0Dgj3rXh6O7Ro0k%3D%2F1902x764%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX4RH5P5GIZEYJE24NTSFUW3IDE.jpg&h=2e4381bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【三權分立防獨裁被刪】■《明名高中通識教育》「應試特訓」練習中，原版一項資料提及三權分立可防政府獨裁，修訂後換成描述香港根據《基本法》享有獨立的司法權和終審權等文字。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/H9NXwCCU8iqRxZSj78Q4QVxWUFg=/1344x840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MQ6RJ4FNLRGYRIRV3QMMNRIFZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FH9NXwCCU8iqRxZSj78Q4QVxWUFg%3D%2F1344x840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMQ6RJ4FNLRGYRIRV3QMMNRIFZY.jpg&h=df084ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【李波被擄變「自願送中」】■《明名高中通識教育》原版一幅專欄漫畫被抽起，改為一則新聞報道，講述警方引述李波稱自願到內地，不涉綁架及銷案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZZXFpxNLhq71AqGVAuLrE-r-hLU=/2937x1630/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YZBTEH6HURA3ZELCLGS2NUWLXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZZXFpxNLhq71AqGVAuLrE-r-hLU%3D%2F2937x1630%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYZBTEH6HURA3ZELCLGS2NUWLXM.jpg&h=926bf188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【梁振英UGL事件消失】■《明名高中通識教育》原版講述獨立調查委員會時，引用前特首梁振英收受澳洲企業UGL公司5,000萬元事件作例子，修訂後被刪除。"}]}